Router_MAIN

enable
configure terminal
ipv6 unicast-routing

interface Serial 0/3/0
no shutdown
ip address 99.99.90.1 255.255.255.0
interface Serial 0/3/1
no shutdown
ip address 99.99.91.1 255.255.255.0
interface Serial 0/2/0
no shutdown
ip address 99.99.92.1 255.255.255.0
ipv6 address 7a4c:15e9::1/126
exit

ip route 193.128.40.0 255.255.255.240 99.99.90.2
ip route 193.128.43.0 255.255.255.240 99.99.91.2
ip route 193.128.44.0 255.255.255.240 99.99.92.2
ipv6 route 2a02:ab8:4521::/48 7a4c:15e9::2